Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get back my lost memories, we traveled to the land of Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There, the Door of Memories was opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Behind it lies the Egyptian world three thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I really the Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the priests who look a lot like Kaiba and Ishizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here, Bakura and I will start the Ultimate Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Thief King, Bakura!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you value your lives, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mahado?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Millennium Ring has detected a great Power of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet, Yugi...\N Or should I say, {\i1}Pharaoh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get the game started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lowly thief...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we are here, you will not lay even one finger upon the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wanna fight against me {\i1}first?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me... Looks like all the Millennium Items are here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Items...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... I'll just take all of your Millennium Items as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Labyrinth inside the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Door of Truth that connects to my other self's memories lies inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if those who do not wield Millennium Items enter that labyrinth in his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cannot return unless they find the True Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of that, do you still wish to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter... Let's go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for that True Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't put your lives in anymore danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we may not even find the other me or that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're wasting time, the other Yugi may..!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made up our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, everyone, please hold hands and concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me... We're going to save you, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millennium Ankh, use your power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to guide us into the labyrinth dwelling within the Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think you guys're strong enough to stop {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, lowly thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These seven Millennium Items have maintained order in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people qualified\N to hold these items...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are us priests, who have trained our souls and the Divine Pharaoh who rules this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a person like {\i1}you{\i0}, with a heart of {\i1}evil{\i0}, were to touch a Millennium Item,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your very soul would burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gods {\i1}themselves{\i0} would punish you with {\i1}death{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying it like {\i1}that{\i0} only makes me even {\i1}more excited{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I want them even {\i1}more{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we will use our powers and make you suffer the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing the lot of you hardly harbors any benefits for me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me your Millennium Items obediently and be my followers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I'm not just spouting bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take these in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me..!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there! It's a bit early to be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got more gifts coming your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Akhenamkhanen's coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vile creature...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you touch the previous Pharaoh's body in such a manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous Pharaoh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... my... father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will {\i1}not{\i0} be forgiven, wretched scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Tablet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you about to do with {\i1}that thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petty thief, your boasting shall come to an end right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Be careful, Shada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalim...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how the\N Millennium Scales are tilting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't weigh that man's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in his heart is unmeasurable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is terrifying evil residing in his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millennium Ankh! Lead me into this sinner's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Ka{\i0} inside him..!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Shada?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Ka{\i0} inside him is way too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Stone is too small for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! His {\i1}Ka{\i0} is about to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this {\i1}Ka{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it! How can such a demon dwell within a mere thief's soul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the {\i1}matter{\i0}, you scum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has my Diabound given you a good {\i1}scare{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Don't underestimate the power of the Millennium Items, thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of the Millennium Rod...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I cast you into the Holy Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully, the power of the Millennium Rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think I'd become a "good person"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after sealing the embrasure within me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Tablet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get up, Honda, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my other self's Soul Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have entered the room of the Pharaoh's soul by the power of the Millennium Ankh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the True Door is somewhere in {\i1}here{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start searching!\N Search the hell outta this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for us, Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll find the True Door and follow you to the world of memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi went to Egypt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, and apart from Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katsuya Jounouchi, Hiroto Honda and Anzu Masaki have gone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi is in Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll give {\i0}this{\i1} to you to make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is your invitation to the Ultimate Dark Game we will be competing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:10:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But aren't you at least a {\i0}bit interested{\i1} in the connection between you and Blue-Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sealing stones are {\i1}useless{\i0} against my Diabound!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vile cur! We will let you witness the true powers of us six High Priests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yes!\N -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there Duel Disks in this age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Duel Disks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are seven "Shrine of {\i1}Wedju{\i0}" sanctuaries surrounding the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to summon the servant {\i1}Ka{\i0} in those tablets...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the true display of our country's alchemical skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The DiaDhanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DiaDhanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They pulled out something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, the enemy is strong... if we don't join forces-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I alone will be enough to resolve this petty matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon the {\i1}Ka{\i0} lying asleep in my Shrine of {\i1}Wedju{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to our side and become our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This has to be..!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galestgoras, I summon thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm seeing now is exactly like a Duel Monsters Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Galestgoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rip Diabound to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Duelists already exist back in this age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm seeing now is exactly like a Duel Monsters Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Duelists already exist back in this age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Galestgoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap him in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falcos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Falcos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unthinkable...! He actually had another {\i1}Ka{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was summoned from the Shrine of {\i1}Wedju{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he able to summon separate {\i1}Ka{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys forgetting something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was lying there in\N Akhenamkhanen's tomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This {\i0}thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the DiaDhank belonging to King Akhenamkhanen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were {\i1}many{\i0} of them in Akhenamkhanen's tomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone slabs lining the shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something you've summoned from King Akhenamkhanen's tomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are tainting the holiness of the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Holy Pharaoh", my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenamkhanen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the {\i1}last{\i0} person I'd call that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he create the Millennium Items you're all wearing to gain {\i1}evil power!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My father was the one who created the Millennium Items?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great King Akhenamkhanen put an end to wars between countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought {\i1}peace{\i0} to this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he wished for a {\i1}millennium{\i0} of peace for this war-torn country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why he left these Millennium Items behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Akhenamkhanen wanted to\N {\i1}stamp out{\i0} all evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To {\i1}purge{\i0} all sinners of their wrong-doings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left us these seven holy items imbued with the power of {\i1}justice{\i0} and {\i1}righteousness{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Peace and justice{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me {\i1}laugh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the holders of the Millennium Items gain great powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those items also respond to the darkness in the holders' heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and drags them into\N the World of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the problem-makers they can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you place the seven Millennium Items on the stone tablet in the village of Kul Elna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One can gain the powers \Nof the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village of Kul Elna, you say..?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does this person\N know of that village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}E-Everyone who knows about that village should be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any of you doesn't believe what I say, go and try it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, the Pharaoh will be nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you'll {\i1}truly{\i0}\N gain the powers of a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence your tongue of this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, do not listen to his words!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insulting the Millennium Items is no different than insulting us directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you want to die so badly, I'll crush you all to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zelua!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gadius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenamkhanen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing but a piss-level {\i1}Ka{\i0}, anyway...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my Diabound is {\i1}worlds apart{\i0} from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not drop your guard, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Mahado! Your {\i1}Ka{\i0} is not powerful enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll summon forth a new servant,\N the Centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the sacred powers\N of the Millennium Scales,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will combine both Minotaur and Centaur into a new {\i1}Ka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Fusion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Fusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, Minocentaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minocentaur, attack Diabound!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}annoying{\i0} me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My servant, Magus of Illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate your Special Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Binding Illusion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think too little of Diabound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a thing to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just him alone, and our priests are..!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your level just wasn't enough to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Ultimate Dark Game you were talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring this to "game over" already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet you and your priests in the afterlife, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiria!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You..!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} why I said that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, this was all \Nyour level was worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move your dirty foot this {\i1}instant{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, it's too dangerous!\N Please step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura, how is this the Ultimate Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such senseless murder, plunder and destruction can hardly be called that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you've done\N just makes me want to {\i1}barf{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, {\i1}excuse me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't remember him, this must be quite the {\i1}emotional{\i0} reunion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, King Akhenamkhanen! To think you'd return to the palace in such a manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me, Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I served King Akhenamkhanen for many years and so I swear upon my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father spent his life fighting to keep peace in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an honorable king!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Justice is in the name of the Gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice just now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, to be honest with you, I myself have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what the rules of this\N Ultimate Dark Game are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's one thing I know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, that the seven Millennium Items are already in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to snatch them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone is my requirement to win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put an end to this right now, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bark all you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura, you've forgotten one {\i1}very{\i0} important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strongest servants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Three Illusionary Beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Illusionary Beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... {\i1}The{\i0} legendary Three Illusionary Beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three Gods that are sealed in the tablets within the Pharaoh's shrine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But their real names are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been said that only the chosen Pharaoh would know their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Can this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this new Pharaoh can control them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll Summon them in the name of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strongest servant, the Three Illusionary Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Justice is in the name of the Gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your words, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow before the Gods, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Hand Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes is weeping...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the other Yugi's world of lost memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, the Ultimate Dark Game between him and the dark personality of Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we are now inside the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we made it into the labyrinth...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no idea how to find the correct door of truth that leads to the other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please guide us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mahado's Resolve"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
